    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "As far as I remember, there are 2 levels of select priority right now - combat units and non-combat (trucks, engineers, minelayers, mcvs). So if there is a select special command it should only be confined to those, otherwise it gets confusing and unintuitive on what's special and what is not. I.e. why is aircraft special? What about Tanya or Chrono Tanks? And Missile Subs, are they special?"
  },
