    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I guess players are not aware how selection priority works... so the discussion need not be very wide - modders should be included though. \r\n\r\nI think changing the system makes sense. Going from arbitrary numbers to predefined categories. Something like say:\r\n- Buildings\r\n- Support (non-combat)\r\n- Low priority combat (aircraft)\r\n- Combat\r\n\r\nThough the current priority system is actually quite clever. And the categories may not fit all use-cases."
